Studies on the effect of photoanode thickness found that performance of DSSC was weak at smaller thicknesses. Electron injection was delayed, and quantum confinement caused a shift in the bottom conduction band towards vacuum [9]. As thickness is increased, short-circuit current, JSC and efficiency, η\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
